Package com.ibm.streams.beam.sdk.io

Defines IBM Streams-specific transforms for PubSub and an I/O connector for IBM Cloud Object Storage services

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SwiftFileSystemOptions
    Options used to configure IBM Cloud Object Storage Swift.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SwiftFileSystemOptionsRegistar
    Register SwiftFileSystemOptions, allowing SwiftFileSystemOptions to be shown in Beam help messages.
    SwiftFileSystemRegistrar
    AutoService registrar for the SwiftFileSystem.
    SwiftResourceId
    ResourceId implementation for IBM Cloud Object Storage Swift for a Beam FileSystem using the swift:// prefix.
    Topic
    Transformations for publishing to or subscribing from other IBM Streams or Beam applications.
    Topic.Publish<T>
    A Publish transform publishes a PCollection for other Beam pipelines and IBM Streams applications to subscribe from it.
    Topic.Subscribe<T>
    A Subscribe transform reads from streams published by other IBM Streams or Beam applications and creates a PCollection.
